com.epoch.db

Class CanonicalizedUnitRW

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epoch.db.DBCommon
      • com.epoch.db.CanonicalizedUnitRW
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CanonicalizedUnitConstants

    public final class CanonicalizedUnitRW
extends DBCommon
implements CanonicalizedUnitConstants
    Contains all database read and write operations pertaining to conversions of one unit to another. All methods are static.
